1132
01:14:23.100 --> 01:14:24.640
Becky.

1133
01:14:26.400 --> 01:14:27.900
Becky!

1134
01:14:32.600 --> 01:14:34.110
Becky?

1135
01:14:35.500 --> 01:14:36.950
Becky, em đâu rồi?!

1136
01:14:37.000 --> 01:14:39.690
Em đây, Miles.

1137
01:14:42.200 --> 01:14:43.200
Em đã không ngủ đấy chứ?

1138
01:14:43.300 --> 01:14:45.300
